OL,3,CDetectives believe missing man 'may
OL,4,Chave been murdered'
OL,6,FAlthough no body has been found,
OL,7,Ffollowing their investigation,
OL,8,Fofficers believe Martin may have come
OL,9,Fto harm.
OL,11,FFour people have since been arrested
OL,12,Fon suspicion of murder including a 44-
OL,13,Fyear-old woman, and man, 23, from
OL,14,FChester, who both remain in custody.
OL,16,FA 35-year-old woman from Winsford and
OL,17,Fa man, 37, from Northwich, have been
OL,18,Freleased on bail.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
