OL,3,CDetectives believe missing man 'may
OL,4,Chave been murdered'
OL,6,FPolice are continuing to investigate
OL,7,FMartin's disappearance and are urging
OL,8,Fanyone with any information, no matter
OL,9,Fhow small, to get in touch.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Andrea Price said:
OL,12,F"Martin was last seen over four months
OL,13,Fago, and during that time we have been
OL,14,Ffollowing multiple lines of enquiries
OL,15,Fin an effort to trace him. We now
OL,16,Fbelieve he may have come to harm.
OL,18,F"Following an extensive investigation,
OL,19,Fwe have now arrested four people in
OL,20,Frelation to his disappearance who are
OL,21,Fassisting us with our enquiries.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
